- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed technique can be applied to various AI tasks, such as classification and prediction. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper deals with graph embeddings, which are commonly used in network analysis and social network analysis. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper provides theoretical results on the optimal regime for the proposed technique, which involves analyzing the computational complexity of the algorithm. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper presents an empirical evaluation on a real-world clinical cohort, which suggests that the proposed technique can be applied to image analysis and computer vision tasks.
